snippet.textDisplay: This song originally sung by Salim Raza ( an unforgettable, old pioneer in Pakistani films) is an immortal melody production-wise. But the new innovation by Coke Studio is also stands as a memorable version by the combinations, variations of symphonies by both vocals and the whole team aimed at individual expertise and performance. Bravo Ali ! I am your father's friend. Long live. Regards to your parents, Ali !
